title: Various Artists - Indie 69 October 2013 New Music Monthly
description:
October is here already. 

This is a huge one, almost double sized, but it plays SO well
from beginning to end. Thanks to Criznittle (HUGE thanks) I finally
got the playlist file to work again. I know what I was doing wrong now,
but it used to work on multiple machines. Guess I will never know
for sure why what happened happened...

So... *fingers crossed*.

Hope it works for YOU.

Try to listen to the m3u file and listen to the whole thing. There are
some GREAT tracks all through the whole thing. Hope you all love it.

See you in November.
